{"lemma":"خَبِير","slug":"خَبِير","root":"خ.ب.ر","root_slug":"خ-ب-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-ب-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"خَبِير","root":"خبر","pos":"N","occurrence_count":45},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["adj","name","noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n9899"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%B1"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"knowing, aware, well-informed"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"experienced, proficient"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"expert, specialist"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"consultant"},{"pos":"name","gloss":"Al-Khabir, \"the All Aware\", one of the names of God in Islam"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"فَعِيل (faʕīl)-type stative-verb derived from the active participle from the verb خَبُرَ (ḵabura)."},"ipa":["/xa.biːr/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n9899","headword_ar":"خَبِيرٌ","root":"xbr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Knowing; having knowledge;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Msb;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xabirN","text_ar":"خَبِرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (AHn:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"possessing much knowledge with respect to internal things;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ahiydN","text_ar":"شَهِيدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"with respect to external things: (L in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$hd","text_ar":"شهد"},{"kind":"text","text":":) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"possessing knowledge of matters of information, news, tidings, accounts, narratives, or stories; of what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xabarN","text_ar":"خَبَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of what are termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axobaAr","text_ar":"اَخْبَار"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAbirN","text_ar":"خَابِرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xabirN","text_ar":"خَبِرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) which last is thought by ISd to be a possessive [as distinguished from a verbal] epithet, (TA,) [or it is from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xabira","text_ar":"خَبِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", a form which ISd may not have known,] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuborN","text_ar":"خُبْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) which is an intensive epithet: (TA:) also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"informed; possessing information."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anaA bihi","text_ar":"اَنَا بِهِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xabiyrN","text_ar":"خَبِيرٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have knowledge of it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) And [hence]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxabiyru","text_ar":"الخَبِيرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a name of God, meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He who knoweth what hath been and what is or will be:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He who well knoweth the internal qualities of things."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sharh Et-Tirmidhee.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Possessing knowledge of God,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by being acquainted with his names and his attributes."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A lawyer; one skilled in the law,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"practical religion."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A head,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"chief."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A tiller,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cultivator, of land."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fur,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"soft hair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wabarN","text_ar":"وَبَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) of camels, and (tropical:)  of the wild ass. (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Hair that has fallen:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a portion thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xabiyrapN","text_ar":"خَبِيرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"below.] ―         -b3-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Plants,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"herbage;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fresh herbage:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) likened to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wabar","text_ar":"وَبَر"},{"kind":"text","text":"of camels, because growing like the latter: and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"seed-produce."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) It is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nasotaxolibu Alxabiyra","text_ar":"نَسْتَخْلِبُ الخَبِيرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We cut"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the reaping-hook,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and eat, the plants,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"herbage."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Froth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foam:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"froth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foam, of the mouths of camels."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA.)       -A4-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Seasoned,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made savoury."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuborapN","text_ar":"خُبْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["AHn","K","TA","S"]}]}}